title: TikTok Parent ByteDance Turns Operating Profit, Sees Revenue Slow
description: The company reported an operating profit of more than $20 billion as its valuation fell by about 26%.

title: Microsoft CEO Testifies on Limits of AI at Google Trial
description: Satya Nadella said Monday at the antitrust trial against Google that there might be limits to how much artificial intelligence can reshape the internet search market.
